  {
   "question": "What are the highest-consensus Restoration Shaman items in Phase 4?",
   "answer": "Totem of Healing Rains (97%), Skyshatter Helmet (94%), Skyshatter Leggings (83%). When an item sits above ~70% among top parsers, treat it as the priority drop to chase."
